company_name: MAG MILCH UND MARKTFRUCHT GRESSOW AKTIENGESELLSCHAFT
information: The company MAG MILCH UND MARKTFRUCHT GRESSOW AKTIENGESELLSCHAFT, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1991, which operates in the Dairy products industry. It also operates in the Cereals and grains industries. It is based in Gressow, Germany.
